data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house built in 2006 offers comfort, style, and convenience. Situated just a 5-minute walk from Buckeye Lake, it presents an ideal opportunity for lakeside living. Well-maintained and ready for you to move in, this property boasts several desirable features: New Water Heater: Enjoy peace of mind with a recently installed water heater. New Water Softener. Large Backyard: Perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing outdoors, the spacious backyard offers ample room for various activities. Features include a patio, covered grilling station, fire pit, covered pergola, and surrounded by a privacy fence. Extra Large Pole Barn: a spacious pole barn with three garage doors. storage space for vehicles, equipment, or hobbies.
